      "source": "https://pitmahistoricalmuseum.weebly.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Pitman Grove Auditorium, a historic meeting hall, entered the National Register of Historic Places in 1977.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
