      ],
      "source": "https://www.pitman.org/about_us/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Pitman Historical Museum, housed in a historic building, showcases the town’s Methodist heritage and hosts lectures year‑round.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        20
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://pitmahistoricalmuseum.weebly.com/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Pitman Theater, a 1920s movie house, remains a local landmark for film lovers.",
